    <section id="message" class="p-index-message">
      <div
        class="p-index-message__inner l-inner u-fadeInDown"
        data-scroll-animation
      >
        <h2
          class="p-index-message__title c-section-title c-section-title--reverse"
        >
          <span>ceo message</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="p-index-message__cols">
          <div class="p-index-message__body">
            <p class="p-index-message__lead">
              <strong>Supporting the revival of Japanese Companies</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="p-index-message__text">
              Japanese companies and the country’s economy as a whole have long
              faced challenges from macroeconomic factors beyond their control,
              such as rapidly changing geopolitical risks, persistent deflation,
              and zero interest rates, leading to currency depreciation and
              reduced purchasing power. Despite these challenges, companies must
              always demonstrate their ability to navigate these macroeconomic
              headwinds and achieve respectable results.
            </p>
            <p class="p-index-message__text">
              In our country, many companies may be grossly underperforming
              relative to their business potential and not fully utilizing the
              capabilities of their management and employees. It is essential
              for these companies to unlock their potential in a way that is
              visible to both their business environment and the capital
              markets. JAC is an investor that supports companies whose
              management is strongly committed to achieving this goal, not just
              as a shareholder but as a dedicated partner in executing their
              initiatives. Japan Activation Capital was established to work
              alongside management to creating prosperous companies with a high
              level of sustainable growth. Once a strong foundation is
              established, the stock market will reward sustainable growth and
              earnings potential, which in turn will inspire other companies to
              follow suit, thereby enhancing the overall competitiveness of
              Japanese companies relative to global peers. We believe the
              collective efforts of these companies will make a positive impact
              on the entire Japanese economy.
            </p>
            <p class="p-index-message__text">
              Japan Activation Capital is dedicated to supporting the
              “Activation” of committed Japanese companies and the Japanese
              economy as a whole.
            </p>
            <div class="p-index-message__sign">
              Chief Executive Officer (Founder)<span>Hiroyuki Otsuka</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <figure class="p-index-message__img c-shadow-item">
            <img
              src="/media/OtsukaCEOM2.jpg"
