    <section id="approach" class="p-index-approach">
      <div class="p-index-approach__bg">
        <div class="p-index-approach__inner l-inner">
          <div class="u-fadeInDown" data-scroll-animation>
            <h2
              class="p-index-approach__title c-section-title c-section-title--white"
            >
              <span>approach</span>
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-index-approach__lead u-fadeInDown"
            data-scroll-animation
          >
            <p>
              Japan Activation Capital was founded by an investment professional
              from a leading global private equity firm who has a strong track
              record of supporting the successful transformation of a number of
              Japanese companies. Together with senior professionals hailing
              from consulting firms, private and public equity funds, investment
              banks, and corporates, as well as senior executives from large
              corporations and financial institutions who have experience
              driving change as operating executives, senior advisors, and
              executive advisors, we intend to leverage our diverse knowledge
              base, experience, and broad network to provide high value-added
              solutions to portfolio companies.
            </p>
            <p>
              Additionally, JAC’s Board of Directors and Investment Advisory
              Committee members are comprised of experienced professionals from
              a variety of backgrounds, who offer an external perspective on
              JAC’s strategic planning, management, and investment decisions.
              This approach helps maximize the value added to our portfolio
              companies while maintaining JAC’s management objectivity.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-index-approach__items">
            <section
              class="p-index-approach__item p-index-approach__item--business u-fadeInUp"
              data-scroll-animation
            >
              <div class="p-index-approach__item-header">
                <h3 class="p-index-approach__item-title">business</h3>
                <p class="p-index-approach__item-lead">
                  Reinforcing execution ability required for business model
                  upgrade to accelerate growth
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-index-approach__item-body">
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    In our country, many companies are undervalued by investors
                    compared to their global peers. This is often due to
                    overexpansion, which dilutes resources, and an excessively
                    risk-averse corporate culture. As a stakeholder, JAC
                    supports management in concentrating resources on core
                    business areas while simultaneously strengthening the
                    business itself, improving profitability and cashflow
                    generation through business portfolio reform.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    Additionally, there is often reluctance to deviate from
                    historically successful business models, stemming from a
                    lack of experience in adapting to changing business
                    environments, which can slow down management’s
                    decision-making. JAC addresses these challenges by offering
                    resources and expertise to accelerate global expansion and
                    new business development, upgrade business models, execution
                    of M&A, and PMI support. Furthermore, our experts in digital
                    transformation, human resource development, and
                    sustainability collaborate closely with management teams,
                    taking a holistic approach to support growth acceleration.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>
            <section
              class="p-index-approach__item p-index-approach__item--sustainability u-fadeInUp"
              data-scroll-animation
            >
              <div class="p-index-approach__item-header">
                <h3 class="p-index-approach__item-title">sustainability</h3>
                <p class="p-index-approach__item-lead">
                  Upgrading businesses to grow alongside Society and the
                  Environment
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-index-approach__item-body">
                <p>
                  Companies must not only respond to risks associated with
                  social and environmental issues but also proactively seek new
                  business opportunities that emerge from them. Businesses that
                  grow in harmony with society and the environment (“Good
                  Growth”) strengthen Japan’s industries and enrich our society.
                  To accelerate Japanese companies’ “Good Growth”, JAC supports
                  the selection, preparation, and execution of initiatives
                  required to enhance growth and corporate value by offering
                  extensive expertise in sustainability and utilizing its global
                  network.
                </p>
                {{# <div class="p-index-approach__item-link"><a href="../en/esg/">Link to ESG Policy Page</a></div> #}}
              </div>
            </section>
            <div class="p-index-approach__cols">
              <section
                class="p-index-approach__item p-index-approach__item--dx u-fadeInUp"
                data-scroll-animation
              >
                <div class="p-index-approach__item-header">
                  <h3 class="p-index-approach__item-title">
                    digital transformation
                  </h3>
                  <p class="p-index-approach__item-lead">
                    Upgrading business models for the era of digital society
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-index-approach__item-body">
                  <p>
                    A digital society involves not only pursuing efficiency
                    through digital technology but also transforming business
                    models into recurring, service-oriented, and data driven
                    agile organizations. However, many companies struggle to
                    advance these initiatives due to a of lack of expertise,
                    conflicts with existing businesses, or concerns about
                    unproven ventures. JAC leverages its extensive resources and
                    network to collaborate with the management of portfolio
                    companies, accelerating business transformation by planning
                    and executing strategies centered on digital technology and
                    creating value through people and organizational
                    development.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </section>
              <section
                class="p-index-approach__item p-index-approach__item--hr u-fadeInUp"
                data-scroll-animation
              >
                <div class="p-index-approach__item-header">
                  <h3 class="p-index-approach__item-title">human resources</h3>
                  <p class="p-index-approach__item-lead">
                    Developing human resources and organizations capable of
                    driving global business management
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-index-approach__item-body">
                  <p>
                    At the root of managing human resources is the belief that
                    individual self-actualization and growth potential play a
                    critical role in corporate and economic activities, as part
                    of a human centric philosophy. Maximizing and realizing
                    individual potential contributes not only to a company’s
                    success but also to the sustainable prosperity and
                    well-being of society. Therefore, it is essential to fully
                    utilize human resources in alignment with the corporate
                    philosophy and promote a compelling “story” to realize its
                    vision. Additionally, to enhance individual growth and
                    motivation, a fair and transparent evaluation and
                    compensation system is a crucial foundation for supporting
                    sustainable corporate transformation. JAC offers a
                    comprehensive range of expert resources to portfolio
                    companies committed to transformation, including
                    recommendations for balanced compensation schemes, and
                    strongly supports their efforts to build a highly
                    competitive organization with effective talent management
                    capabilities.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </section>
              <section
                class="p-index-approach__item p-index-approach__item--ir u-fadeInUp"
                data-scroll-animation
              >
                <div class="p-index-approach__item-header">
                  <h3 class="p-index-approach__item-title">
                    investor relations
                  </h3>
                  <p class="p-index-approach__item-lead">
                    Communicating with capital markets and fostering high
                    expectations from stakeholders
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-index-approach__item-body">
                  <p>
                    JAC supports portfolio companies in nurturing strong
                    relationships with the capital markets by crafting
                    appropriate and effective IR/SR dialogue, as well as helping
                    to develop a new, long-term investor base. JAC’s
                    professionals, equipped with deep market knowledge, support
                    the effective communication of management initiatives
                    related to growth strategies, which leads to higher
                    expectations from the capital markets.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
